    b1 = [0] * (n + 1)
    a1[0] = b1[0] = -math.inf
    m1 = 0

        m2 = min(m2, s2)
    result = []
    for i in range(n):
        ans = max(a1[i], a2[n - i], b1[i] + b2[n - i])
        result.append(ans)
    return result
